	<key>PayloadDescription</key>
	<string>TESTING POSTURE: same security floor as com.hxguardian.unified, with Wi-Fi and Bluetooth visible in Control Center so the operator can toggle them during AnyDesk testing. Bluetooth itself remains disabled by the bluetooth payload — only the Control Center module is un-hidden. Do NOT install on production airgap devices — install com.hxguardian.unified instead.</string>
